OL,3,CFairy door forest founder says vandals
OL,4,Care 'pure evil'
OL,6,FThe man behind a beloved fairy door
OL,7,Fwoodland walk near Truro says repeated
OL,8,Fdamage from vandals is making him
OL,9,Fquestion whether to continue repairing
OL,10,Fthe tiny homes.
OL,12,FJohn Roche started making fairy homes
OL,13,Fand doors for his grandchildren in
OL,14,F2020 during Covid pandemic.
OL,16,FHe got permission from Truro City
OL,17,FCouncil to add his fairy doors to the
OL,18,F'Enchanted Trail' in Malabar woods at
OL,19,FCoosebean just outside of the city.
