OL,6,FHe said: "At the time when there was
OL,7,FCovid (lockdowns during the pandemic),
OL,8,FI thought one good thing for morale is
OL,9,Fwe could sort of put something there,
OL,10,Fand then people can walk down for that
OL,11,Fone hour they were allowed out.
OL,13,F"And of course, the rest of my time is
OL,14,Fspent in the shed scrounging materials
OL,15,Fand various other bits and making more
OL,16,Fdoors."
OL,18,F"I couldn't make them fast enough to
OL,19,Fbe quite honest."
