OL,6,FYet since 2020, there have been
OL,7,F"numerous" spates of vandalism and
OL,8,Frecently as many as eight fairy houses
OL,9,Fhave been "ripped off their hinges off
OL,10,Fthe posts".
OL,12,FJohn says initially when the upcycled
OL,13,Fhomes and doors were broken he would
OL,14,Ftry to make repairs with "stronger
OL,15,Fbolts" but the damage has continued.
OL,17,FHe said: "Some people say it's the
OL,18,Fwind.
