OL,3,CFairy door forest founder says vandals
OL,4,Care 'pure evil'
OL,6,F"It wasn't the wind. I've got proof
OL,7,Fthat the engines have been twisted and
OL,8,Fripped off and thrown in the river."
OL,10,FThe route is loved by all ages with
OL,11,Fmore than 6,000 members on the
OL,12,FFacebook page Fairy doors of Malabar
OL,13,Fand Coosebean.
OL,15,FOver the years John has made fairy
OL,16,Fdoors for more than 10 schools around
OL,17,Fthe city and has been commissioned by
OL,18,Fthose grieving to make bespoke fairy
OL,19,Fhomes in memory of their loved ones.
