OL,4,Care 'pure evil'
OL,6,FThe 73-year-old says he's had a 'black
OL,7,Fcloud' hanging over him every time he
OL,8,Ffinds the houses damaged.
OL,10,FWhile he's prepared to 'freshen up'
OL,11,Fthe houses every now and again, he's
OL,12,Ffrustrated they are not allowed to put
OL,13,Fcameras on the trail to monitor who
OL,14,Fmay be behind the damage.
OL,16,FHe said: "You're not going to get the
OL,17,Fpolice to go and (look into) these
OL,18,Fcrimes, what damage have they done?
