OL,3,CFairy door forest founder says vandals
OL,4,Care 'pure evil'
OL,6,F"They're destroying their memories. To
OL,7,Fbe quite honest, theres's no excuse
OL,8,Ffor it. Pure evil, basically."
OL,10,F"Truro families go down there, you get
OL,11,Flittle children making craft, things,
OL,12,Fwriting letters.
OL,14,F"The fairy bridge of friends at the
OL,15,Fmoment's got 70 children's names on.
OL,16,FPeople do get involved and when you
OL,17,Fgive something to the community, I'm
OL,18,Fhoping that now, the community will
OL,19,Fprobably step in now and take it over."
